                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340102-120-off673 t18340102-120-crimeloc675"></join> - I have seen the prisoner, but do not know him.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. His house is in St. Luke's, and I am indicted for stealing in the parish of Shoreditch.</p>
